## Why This Is Better Than Joining on User
```
Join on recpt/user    →  matches ALL emails to same user — false positives
                         one user gets 100 emails — 100 potential matches
                         gap correlation is imprecise

Join on message_id    →  matches ONE specific email to ONE calendar event
                         zero false positives
                         proves THIS exact email created THIS exact event
                         definitive evidence of the gap
